\par 
\par During the last four weeks, increasing appreciation for "the great effort made by our American ally" in providing us "with the food, the weapons, and the man" has been noted - though "Russia's effort still overshadows them".
\par 
\par "Doubts" still reported about America are as follows:
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid92027 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li426\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin426\itap0\pararsid92027 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484735 
(a) America desires to dominate the world after the war Some (Four Regions) people ask "how much of the Empire has already been ceded to America, and will we ever get it back?"
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid92027 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484735 (b) There is some resentment end distru}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid92027 st of American claims of losses }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484735 
inflicted on the enemy (Three Regions). "The Americans are assuming all the credit for present victories." 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li0\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\pararsid7484735 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484735 
\par American troops in this country: There has been little comment on American troops during the last four weeks. Some praise their "niceness"; but the following familiar criticisms continue to be reported:
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid92027 
\par }\pard \ltrpar\s20\qj \fi-11\li426\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin426\itap0\pararsid92027 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484735 
(a) Their behaviour with women and especially with young (Three Regions). "Due to their efforts children of fourteen and fifteen are with child"; it is thought 
that "American troops arc amenable only to American law". The girls themselves are, however, much blamed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid92027 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7484735 (b) Their high pay (Three Regions) - as a result of which they are accused of ostentation, and of "buying up" everything available including labou
r. The "palatial premises!' and "lavish provision" provided for them are also criticised.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid92027 
